data.description: Beautiful place in the country, just the right size to enjoy! This 7.599 acre property is on a paved county road, just off Hwy 77, near the Minerva community. It is located about midway between Rockdale and Cameron. It is about 50 miles from Austin-Round Rock, 32 miles from Taylor, 40 miles from Temple-Belton and 50 miles from Bryan-college Station.            This property has a 2540 square foot brick home built in 1977. It has 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 2 living areas, formal dining room, office/den and utility room. This property also has a 10 x 20 storage building, 40 x 60 shop / multi use building and a 20 x 40 barn/ cattle shed. It has good pasture, is fully fenced and has a nice pond.        Great Property, Great Location! Lots of peace and quiet. Just waiting for someone to ENJOY!
